    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>For Java 8 and above, it's easy:</p>\n\n<pre><code>when(mock.process(Matchers.anyList()));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>For Java 7 and below, the compiler needs a bit of help. Use <code>anyListOf(Class&lt;T&gt; clazz)</code>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>when(mock.process(Matchers.anyListOf(Bar.class)));\n</code></pre>\n"
