    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Before Java 8 (versions 7 or 6) I use the new method ArgumentMatchers.anyList:</p>\n\n<pre><code>import static org.mockito.Mockito.*;\nimport org.mockito.ArgumentMatchers;\n\nverify(mock, atLeastOnce()).process(ArgumentMatchers.&lt;Bar&gt;anyList());\n</code></pre>\n"
