  "title" : "Mockito: List Matchers with generics",
  "body" : "<p>Mockito offers:</p>\n\n<p></p>\n\n<pre><code>when(mock.process(Matchers.any(List.class)));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p></p>\n\n<p>How to avoid warning if <code>process</code> takes a <code>List&lt;Bar&gt;</code> instead?<br/></p>\n"
